The paper proposes a deep neural network for non-rigid structure from motion, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions handling problems of unprecedented scale and shape complexity, which suggests that it may fall under the graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
